msContents.summary: Copy of a collection of poetry by one author.

supportDesc.extent: 198, i leaves : 294 x 197 (224 x 120) mm, bound to 300 x 205 mm

layoutDesc.layout: 14-16 lines in two columns; borders and columns ruled.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in nastaʻlīq in black ink; pointed.

decoDesc.decoNote: Border-rules in gold, black, red and blue; columns and lines also ruled in gold; rubrications in red.
